Pre-Game Insights: Vladimir Guerrero Jr. and Alec Burleson will be among the stars on display when the Toronto Blue Jays face the St. Louis Cardinals on Sunday at 1:37 p.m. ET, at Rogers Centre.
Bookmakers list the Blue Jays as -127 favorites on the moneyline, while giving the underdog Cardinals +107 moneyline odds.
Toronto is the run-line favorite (-1.5). An 8.5-run over/under has been set for the matchup.
